<title>
DTC Table
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
When ignition is ON or during engine running, DTC is detected by pushing cruise control switch (MAIN (ON/OFF), CANCEL, RES/ACC, or SET/COAST) for more than specified time.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.785in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.374in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.903in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "4.142in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
DTC
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
DTC name
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry namest = "3" nameend = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
DTC detecting condition
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
 P0504 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Brake Switch “A”/“B” Correlation
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry namest = "3" nameend = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Refer to 
<intxref refid = "AENBP70A1104005">DTC Table</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
P0575 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70AA104008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Cruise Control Input Circuit
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry namest = "3" nameend = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
This DTC is detected if any one of the following conditions is met.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Signal voltage of cruise control switch signal circuit is higher than specified voltage for specified time continuously.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ON signals of any or all of following switches of cruise control system are detected for longer than specified time.
</ptxt>
</item>
<list2 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
MAIN (ON/OFF) switch
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
CANCEL switch
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
RES/ACC switch
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
SET/COAST switch
</ptxt>
</item>
</list2>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
P0649 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70AA104009"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Speed Control Lamp Control Circuit
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry namest = "3" nameend = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
“CRUISE” / “SET” indicator light lighting signal from combination meter remains unchanged even if ECM transmits request to turn on or turn off “CRUISE” / “SET” indicator light control signal to combination meter through CAN communication.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
